ght version of the instrument while sword is equiped, bonus to sung songs(i.e. clarity, etc etc) 55% party haste clickable.  Also take a look at bard equipment in general.  They totally designed this stuff for the group.  All velious BP's have SSoT effect for whole party.  Singing steel stuff is the same except for legs and gaunts.  Legs fear, gaunts EB.  No other class was designed to be so group oriented as the bard, part of the reason I chose the class.  So why shouldn't the group support the bard to benefit the group as a whole.  Because they are so loot hungry for their own characters and their clique group within the guild that they fail to see how helping someone who most think of as a nuasance class would be of benefit.  Properly played, a bard can save lives and time.  Suggested reading for anyone that feels the bard is a wasted class is www.eqdiva.com . <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/bayonaero.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=benielsongweaver>Beniel Songweaver</A> at: 12/19/01 5:24:56 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/uedeina.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Edeina</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Arch Board Mistress</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(12/19/01 5:23:36 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=734.topic&index=13>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.one.se/users/chribesk/edeina.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: They said give up your Epic.</span><hr size=1> If your guild won't or can't help you with something you want done, you basically have three choises.<br><br>*Give up your wish for now.<br>